Temporal SNA tools for continuous- and discrete-time longitudinal networks having vertex, edge, and attribute dynamics stored in the 'networkDynamic' format. This work was supported by grant R01HD68395 from the National Institute of Health.

name: r-tsna
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.3.6" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-tsna
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/tsna_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/tsna/tsna_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: c1dd9e5596f42ba742a40ec8fff8d820d9c75674c1976401aee18356a2109074

build:
  number: 1
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-network >=1.13
    - r-networkdynamic >=0.9
    - r-statnet.common
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-network >=1.13
    - r-networkdynamic >=0.9
    - r-statnet.common

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('tsna')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('tsna')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: http://statnet.org
  license: GPL-3.0-only
  summary: Temporal SNA tools for continuous- and discrete-time longitudinal networks having vertex, edge, and attribute dynamics stored in the 'networkDynamic' format. This work was supported by grant R01HD68395 from the National Institute of Health.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
